                                        531
                                18 Kānun I A. Gr.
                                        843
                             the Huns
                             entered  Roman
                                territory  and plundered as far as the area around
                                 Aleppo 
                            and  Antioch .
                         <a href="/8559-531" class="factoid-more">See factoid page
                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-circle-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"/></a></p><hr/><p class="indent"> In 
